</nav>

<!-- MAIN -->
<main class="feed-main">
	<div class="container">

		<!-- HERO -->
		<section class="feed-hero">
			<div class="hero-badge">Updated Monthly</div>
			<h1 class="hero-title">The Wealth Newsfeed</h1>
			<p class="hero-subtitle">Monthly Entrepreneur Spotlight</p>
			<p class="hero-desc">This tab features one entrepreneur each month to inspire users with real stories of growth, persistence, and success.</p>
		</section>

		<!-- THIS MONTH'S FEATURE -->
		<section class="spotlight-card">
			<div class="spotlight-header">
				<div class="spotlight-month-badge">
					<span class="month-icon">⭐</span>
					<span>This Month's Feature</span>
				</div>
				<div class="spotlight-number">#7</div>
			</div>

			<div class="spotlight-name-row">
				<div class="spotlight-avatar">TD</div>
				<div>
					<h2 class="spotlight-name">Tyler Dikman</h2>
					<div class="spotlight-tag">Young Entrepreneur &middot; Tech &middot; CoolTronics</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="spotlight-divider"></div>

			<div class="spotlight-story">
				<p>Tyler Dikman started showing entrepreneurial drive at a very young age. By age five, he was already exploring business ideas through lemonade stands, lawn mowing, babysitting, and even a magic show business. At 15, he launched <strong>CoolTronics</strong>, a computer repair business that grew quickly and reached <strong>one million dollars</strong> in sales.</p>
				<p>His story is a reminder that curiosity, consistency, and action can turn small ideas into something much bigger.</p>
			</div>

			<!-- KEY HIGHLIGHTS -->
			<div class="highlight-grid">
				<div class="highlight-item">
					<div class="highlight-value">Age 5</div>
					<div class="highlight-label">First business ideas</div>
				</div>
				<div class="highlight-item">
					<div class="highlight-value">Age 15</div>
					<div class="highlight-label">Launched CoolTronics</div>
				</div>
				<div class="highlight-item">
					<div class="highlight-value">$1M+</div>
					<div class="highlight-label">In sales</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- TAKEAWAY -->
			<div class="takeaway">
				<div class="takeaway-icon">💡</div>
				<p>Curiosity, consistency, and action can turn small ideas into something much bigger.</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- COMPACT CARD VERSION -->
		<section class="glass-card">
			<div class="section-header">
				<span class="section-icon">📱</span>
				<h3 class="section-title">Quick View</h3>
			</div>
			<div class="compact-card">
				<div class="compact-top">
					<div class="compact-avatar">TD</div>
					<div class="compact-info">
						<div class="compact-name">Tyler Dikman</div>
						<div class="compact-label">Entrepreneur Spotlight #7</div>
					</div>
					<div class="compact-badge">This Month</div>
				</div>
				<p class="compact-text">Tyler Dikman began building businesses as a child and launched CoolTronics at 15. What started as a small computer repair idea grew into a million-dollar company, showing how early ambition can lead to real success.</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- WHAT THIS FEATURE IS -->
		<section class="glass-card about-feature">
			<div class="section-header">
				<span class="section-icon">📰</span>
				<h3 class="section-title">About the Wealth Newsfeed</h3>
			</div>
			<p class="about-text">A simple content feature designed to bring the website to life with monthly motivation from entrepreneurs of all ages around the world. Each month, the tab highlights one inspiring person and a short story about their journey, growth, and success.</p>
			<div class="about-pillars">
				<div class="pillar">
					<div class="pillar-icon">🌍</div>
					<div class="pillar-label">Global stories</div>
				</div>
				<div class="pillar">
					<div class="pillar-icon">👶→👨‍💼</div>
					<div class="pillar-label">All ages</div>
				</div>
				<div class="pillar">
					<div class="pillar-icon">📅</div>
					<div class="pillar-label">Updated monthly</div>
				</div>
				<div class="pillar">
					<div class="pillar-icon">🔥</div>
					<div class="pillar-label">Real journeys</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- PAST SPOTLIGHTS TEASER -->
		<section class="glass-card">
			<div class="section-header">
				<span class="section-icon">📚</span>
				<h3 class="section-title">Coming Soon</h3>
			</div>
			<div class="coming-soon-grid">
				<div class="coming-item">
					<div class="coming-num">#8</div>
					<div class="coming-text">Next month's spotlight</div>
					<div class="coming-tag">August 2026</div>
				</div>
				<div class="coming-item">
					<div class="coming-num">📂</div>
					<div class="coming-text">Past spotlights archive</div>
					<div class="coming-tag">Coming soon</div>
				</div>
				<div class="coming-item">
					<div class="coming-num">🗳️</div>
					<div class="coming-text">Nominate an entrepreneur</div>
					<div class="coming-tag">Coming soon</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

	</div>
</main>

<!-- FOOTER -->
<footer class="footer">
	<div class="container">
		<p class="footer-copy">&copy; 2026 Financial Literacy Extraordinaire. All rights reserved.</p>
		<div class="footer-links">
			<a href="/">Home</a><span class="footer-dot"></span>
			<a href="/about">About</a><span class="footer-dot"></span>
			<a href="/#features">Features</a><span class="footer-dot"></span>
			<a href="/#faq">Contact</a>
		</div>
		<p class="footer-tagline">Club FLE — Master Your Money. Build Your Future.</p>
	</div>
</footer>

<script>
	document.getElementById('burger')?.addEventListener('click', () => {
		document.getElementById('navLinks')?.classList.toggle('open');
	});
</script>

</body>
</html>

<style>
:root{
	--bg:#0A0A12;--purple:#7B2FF2;--orange:#FF6B35;--gold:#FFD23F;--cyan:#4FD1E8;
	--font:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,'Helvetica Neue',Arial,sans-serif;
}
*,*::before,*::after{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
body{font-family:var(--font);color:#D8D8E8;background:var(--bg);line-height:1.6;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;overflow-x:hidden}
a{text-decoration:none;color:inherit}
.container{max-width:820px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px}

@keyframes twinkle-a{0%{opacity:.3}100%{opacity:.9}}
@keyframes twinkle-b{0%{opacity:.85}100%{opacity:.3}}
@keyframes grid-crawl{0%{background-position:0 0}100%{background-position:60px 60px}}
@keyframes shimmer{0%{background-position:-200% 0}100%{background-position:200% 0}}

.grid-bg{position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:0;pointer-events:none;background-image:linear-gradient(rgba(123,47,242,.03) 1px,transparent 1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(123,47,242,.03) 1px,transparent 1px);background-size:60px 60px;animation:grid-crawl 22s linear infinite}
.pg-stars{position:fixed;inset:0;pointer-events:none;z-index:0}
.pg-stars-sm{animation:twinkle-a 3s ease-in-out infinite alternate;box-shadow:42px 38px 0 .5px rgba(255,255,255,.7),310px 24px 0 .5px rgba(255,255,255,.6),520px 62px 0 .5px rgba(255,255,255,.8),680px 88px 0 .5px rgba(255,255,255,.55),920px 42px 0 .5px rgba(255,255,255,.65),85px 320px 0 .5px rgba(255,255,255,.6),375px 350px 0 .5px rgba(255,255,255,.7)}
.pg-stars-md{animation:twinkle-b 5s ease-in-out infinite alternate;box-shadow:95px 65px 0 .75px rgba(255,255,255,.75),440px 48px 0 .75px rgba(255,255,255,.8),810px 80px 0 .75px rgba(255,255,255,.65),380px 250px 0 .75px rgba(255,255,255,.7),720px 410px 0 .75px rgba(255,255,255,.75)}

/* NAV */
.nav{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;z-index:200;background:rgba(10,10,18,.65);backdrop-filter:blur(24px);-webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(24px);border-bottom:1px solid rgba(123,47,242,.1)}
.nav-inner{max-width:1180px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;height:72px}
.logo{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;font-weight:800;font-size:1.2rem;z-index:201}
.logo-icon{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;width:38px;height:38px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--purple),var(--orange));border-radius:11px;font-weight:900;font-size:1.1rem;color:#fff}
.logo-word{color:#fff;letter-spacing:-.3px}
.nav-links{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:24px;font-size:.85rem;font-weight:500}
.nav-links a{color:rgba(255,255,255,.6);transition:color .25s}
.nav-links a:hover,.nav-links a.active{color:#fff}
.nav-btn{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--purple),var(--orange));color:#fff!important;padding:10px 24px;border-radius:10px;font-weight:700;transition:transform .3s,box-shadow .3s;box-shadow:0 0 18px rgba(123,47,242,.3)}
.nav-btn:hover{transform:translateY(-2px) scale(1.05);box-shadow:0 0 30px rgba(123,47,242,.5)}
.burger{display:none;flex-direction:column;gap:5px;background:none;border:none;cursor:pointer;padding:4px;z-index:201}
.burger span{display:block;width:24px;height:2px;background:#fff;border-radius:2px}

.feed-main{position:relative;z-index:1;padding:100px 0 60px;min-height:80vh}

/* HERO */
.feed-hero{text-align:center;margin-bottom:40px}
.hero-badge{display:inline-block;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:3px;color:#fbbf24;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:14px;padding:6px 16px;border-radius:20px;background:rgba(245,158,11,0.1);border:1px solid rgba(245,158,11,0.2)}
.hero-title{font-size:38px;font-weight:800;margin:0 0 8px;font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#e0c3ff,#fbbf24,#f59e0b);-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent}
.hero-subtitle{font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#d4b4ff;margin:0 0 12px;letter-spacing:0.5px}
.hero-desc{font-size:15px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.45);max-width:500px;margin:0 auto;line-height:1.7}

/* GLASS CARDS */
.glass-card{background:rgba(18,10,32,0.65);backdrop-filter:blur(18px);-webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(18px);border:1px solid rgba(160,120,255,0.15);border-radius:16px;padding:28px;margin-bottom:20px;box-shadow:0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.3),inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.04)}

/* SECTION HEADERS */
.section-header{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:18px}
.section-icon{font-size:20px}
.section-title{font-size:16px;font-weight:800;color:#e0c3ff;margin:0}

/* SPOTLIGHT CARD */
.spotlight-card{background:rgba(18,10,32,0.7);backdrop-filter:blur(20px);-webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(20px);border:1px solid rgba(245,158,11,0.2);border-radius:20px;padding:32px;margin-bottom:24px;box-shadow:0 0 40px rgba(245,158,11,0.06),0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.3),inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.04)}

.spotlight-header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;margin-bottom:24px}
.spotlight-month-badge{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#fbbf24;padding:8px 16px;border-radius:10px;background:rgba(245,158,11,0.1);border:1px solid rgba(245,158,11,0.2)}
.month-icon{font-size:16px}
.spotlight-number{font-size:14px;font-weight:800;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.2);letter-spacing:1px}

.spotlight-name-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:18px;margin-bottom:24px}
.spotlight-avatar{width:64px;height:64px;border-radius:18px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#b47aff,#f59e0b);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:22px;font-weight:800;color:#fff;flex-shrink:0;box-shadow:0 0 24px rgba(180,122,255,0.2)}
.spotlight-name{font-size:26px;font-weight:800;color:#fff;margin:0 0 4px;font-family:'Playfair Display',serif}
.spotlight-tag{font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.4);font-weight:500;letter-spacing:0.3px}

.spotlight-divider{height:1px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,rgba(245,158,11,0.2),transparent);margin-bottom:24px}

.spotlight-story p{font-size:15px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);line-height:1.85;margin:0 0 16px}
.spotlight-story p:last-child{margin-bottom:0}
.spotlight-story strong{color:#fbbf24;font-weight:700}

/* HIGHLIGHTS */
.highlight-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:12px;margin:28px 0}
.highlight-item{text-align:center;padding:18px 14px;border-radius:14px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.02);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06)}
.highlight-value{font-size:24px;font-weight:800;color:#fbbf24;margin-bottom:4px}
.highlight-label{font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.4);font-weight:500}

/* TAKEAWAY */
.takeaway{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:14px;padding:18px 22px;border-radius:14px;background:rgba(180,122,255,0.06);border:1px solid rgba(180,122,255,0.15);margin-top:24px}
.takeaway-icon{font-size:22px;margin-top:1px;flex-shrink:0}
.takeaway p{margin:0;font-size:14px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.65);line-height:1.7;font-style:italic}

/* COMPACT CARD */
.compact-card{padding:20px;border-radius:14px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.02);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06)}
.compact-top{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:14px}
.compact-avatar{width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:12px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#b47aff,#f59e0b);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:14px;font-weight:800;color:#fff;flex-shrink:0}
.compact-info{flex:1}
.compact-name{font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:rgba(255,255,255,.9)}
.compact-label{font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.35)}
.compact-badge{font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1px;color:#fbbf24;text-transform:uppercase;padding:4px 10px;border-radius:8px;background:rgba(245,158,11,0.1);border:1px solid rgba(245,158,11,0.15)}
.compact-text{margin:0;font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.55);line-height:1.7}

/* ABOUT */
.about-text{font-size:14px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.55);line-height:1.8;margin:0 0 20px}
.about-pillars{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:10px}
.pillar{text-align:center;padding:14px 10px;border-radius:12px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.02);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05)}
.pillar-icon{font-size:20px;margin-bottom:6px}
.pillar-label{font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.45);font-weight:600}

/* COMING SOON */
.coming-soon-grid{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px}
.coming-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;padding:14px 18px;border-radius:12px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.02);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06)}
.coming-num{font-size:16px;font-weight:800;color:#b47aff;width:36px;text-align:center;flex-shrink:0}
.coming-text{flex:1;font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.6);font-weight:500}
.coming-tag{font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.25);text-transform:uppercase}

/* FOOTER */
.footer{position:relative;z-index:1;padding:48px 0;background:var(--bg);border-top:1px solid rgba(123,47,242,.08);text-align:center}
.footer-copy{font-size:.85rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.3);margin-bottom:16px}
.footer-links{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:8px;margin-bottom:16px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.footer-links a{font-size:.85rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.4);transition:color .25s}
.footer-links a:hover{color:var(--gold)}
.footer-dot{width:4px;height:4px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(255,255,255,.15)}
.footer-tagline{font-size:.75rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.18);letter-spacing:.5px}

@media(max-width:768px){
	.nav-links{position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:200;background:rgba(10,10,18,.97);backdrop-filter:blur(24px);-webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(24px);flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;gap:28px;font-size:1.3rem;opacity:0;pointer-events:none;transition:opacity .3s}
	.nav-links.open{opacity:1;pointer-events:auto}
	.burger{display:flex}
	.feed-main{padding:88px 0 40px}
	.hero-title{font-size:28px}
	.spotlight-card{padding:24px}
	.spotlight-name{font-size:22px}
	.highlight-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
	.about-pillars{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}
}
</style>
